NeoGraph Third-Party Licenses
==============================

This file contains the licenses for all third-party libraries bundled with
NeoGraph or fetched at build time. Summary:

  * Bundled under `deps/` (vendored): yyjson, Taskflow, cpp-httplib,
    moodycamel::ConcurrentQueue, Clay.
  * Vendored C glue file only (library itself pulled at build time):
    Clay's raylib renderer (`deps/clay_renderer_raylib.c`) + raylib
    (FetchContent, optional, used only by example 11 `clay_chatbot`).
  * System dependency (not bundled): OpenSSL, required by cpp-httplib
    for HTTPS.

yyjson is compiled (C source), everything else bundled is header-only.


